IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. INTEREST-CALC.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 PRINCIPAL        PIC 9(7)V99 VALUE 0.
01 RATE             PIC 9(3)V99 VALUE 0.
01 TIME-YEARS       PIC 9(2)    VALUE 0.
01 INTEREST         PIC 9(7)V99 VALUE 0.
01 TOTAL-AMOUNT     PIC 9(7)V99 VALUE 0.

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    MOVE 7000.00  TO PRINCIPAL
    MOVE 7.50     TO RATE
    MOVE 3        TO TIME-YEARS

    COMPUTE INTEREST = (PRINCIPAL * RATE * TIME-YEARS) / 100
    COMPUTE TOTAL-AMOUNT = PRINCIPAL + INTEREST

    DISPLAY "Principal Amount : $" PRINCIPAL
    DISPLAY "Interest Rate    : " RATE "%"
    DISPLAY "Time Period      : " TIME-YEARS " years"
    DISPLAY "Interest Earned  : $" INTEREST
    DISPLAY "Total Amount     : $" TOTAL-AMOUNT

    STOP RUN.
